=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 7f434e16-aabe-314d-88f0-fac7d3f26d51</guid><dc:creator>瓦伦蒂娜·帕拉迪诺，Cherlynn Low</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 16 Jun 2023 17:00:08 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686934808</ingested><modified> 2023-06-16T17:00:25+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[news]]></category><category><![CDATA[smartwatch]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[thebuyersguide]]></category><category><![CDATA[Samsung]]></category><category><![CDATA[commerce]]></category><category><![CDATA[Fitbit]]></category><category><![CDATA[gear]]></category><category><![CDATA[ElectronicEquipment,Instruments&Components]]></category><category><![CDATA[ElectronicsAccessories]]></category><category><![CDATA[OfficeElectronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology&Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Valentina Palladino]]></category><media:content height="1204" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-12/45544550-7c97-11ed-be7f-b301bffa0c0d" width="1753"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1204" medium="image"